<BLOCK1><TI>ORDER</TI>
<P>THE APPEAL from the order of the Honourable Mr. Justice R. Punnett of the Supreme Court of British Columbia at Victoria, British Columbia dated March 2, 2018 coming on for hearing on December 11, 2018, AND ON HEARING Deborah Strachan, Q.C. and Amanda Lord, counsel for the Appellant, and Steven M. Kelliher and Declan C. Redman, counsel for the Respondents, AND ON READING the materials filed herein; AND ON JUDGMENT BEING PRONOUNCED ON THIS DATE;</P>
<P>THIS COURT ORDERS that the appeal is allowed and the order is set aside;</P>
<P>AND THIS COURT FURTHER ORDERS that the underlying action is dismissed.</P>
<P>AND THIS COURT FURTHER ORDERS that the Canada Revenue Agency does recover the costs of the appeal from Tony and Helen Samaroo promptly after assessment.</P>
